  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support for church-led peacebuilding in South Sudan pilot</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">-Context analysis for Yirol and Aweil 
-Capacity assessment of ICCs 
-Monitoring and learning activities of pilot activities
-Planning workshop conducted with ICCs and SSCC
-Follow on to planning workshop &#x2013; consultancy to develop outputs of workshop covering the next year 
-Launch events at local level and initial APP implementation activities as appropriate
-Review and finalisation of plans</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">-Enhanced understanding of how ICCs function and development of appropriate capacity assessment tool
-Enhanced understanding and evidence on how ICCs could be strengthened to implement the APP at the local level, to inform future programming.</narrative>
  </description>
